        <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-3 col-sm-2 hidden-xs"></div>

        <!--address content-->
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 address-container help-container">
          <b>You're currently viewing Coco Cafe's address book! You can do the following actions:</b>
          <br><br>
          <ul style="text-align:left">
            <li>Create a new contact
              <li>Create a new contact through the link in the top right admin bar.</li>
            </li>
            <li>Edit or delete an existing contact
              <li>Navigate back to the home page, click on the contact you would like to modify. Choose the appropriate option from the buttons at the bottom or the admin bar links in the top right.</li>
            </li>
            <li>Sort contact by tags
              <li>Use navigation menu to see all your contacts at once or sort your contacts based on if they're a favorite contact, vendor, or customer.</li>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

